headline: ProAssurance Q3 Earnings Beat on Strong Net Investment Income
summary: PRA's third-quarter earnings benefit from improving underwriting results in its Specialty P&C segment. Declining profits in the Segregated Portfolio Cell Reinsurance unit partially offset the positives.
